Text: NADAThe convention dates are now January Im sending you a new confirmation from the NADA for these dates They are using some of the NFL money to refund of the registration fees for the dealers and managers and of the fees for the guests Of course I registered everyone before September otherwise I would have registered everyone as managers I m sure thats what everyone will do that registers now Who said the early bird gets the worm Dad
